window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The complete series in a single offering!</b></p> <p>Dark forces pull Dan into a world he never imagined was real.</p> <p>Left stranded and alone, he quickly realizes that this unexpected journey comes with a twist. The power of the leylines flows through his body, giving him power unlike any in the world can wield.</p> <p>As he sets out to find the answers of how he came to be in this world, he comes to the aid of a beautiful stranger who becomes his guide—and perhaps more—in this strange place.</p> <p>Will he find answers, or will the evil befouling the land find him first?</p>"; 
